Our Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you use our Resteez Manager mobile application ("App"). 
We are committed to maintaining the privacy and security of your information.
By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.

When you use the App, we may collect personal information such as user name, email address, contact number, and other relevant details provided by you.
We may also collect transactional information related to your use of the App, such as purchase history and food order details.
We use the personal information you provide to authenticate your account, enable you to use the features and functionalities of the App, 
and communicate with you regarding your account and transactions.

The app securely captures and stores images for food listings using your device.

We reserve the right to modify or update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the App or by other means.
